{"word":"μάσσω","slug":"μάσσω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μάσσω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <el>ΜΑΓ</el>, for <el>μάγσω</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to handle, touch</i>, in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>: <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>ἐπιμαίομαι.</el><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to work with the hands, to knead dough</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>pinso</el>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; also in <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>μάττειν ἐπινοίας</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>μᾶζα ὑπ' ἐμοῦ μεμαγμένη</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>σῖτος μεμαγμένος</el> dough <i>ready kneaded</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}